cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL

The paper discusses a technique for document representation and retrieval, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of topic modeling and natural language processing also suggests that it could be classified under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The use of Expectation Maximization (EM) algorithm for training and obtaining accuracy results suggests that it could also be classified under Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL).
